Orion Broadcast Group Inc said itsmajority-owned Orion Financial Services Corp subsidiary hasagreed to purchase FN Realty Services Inc from Ford Motor Cofor 1,200,000 to 1,500,000 dlrs in cash and notes.    It said closing is expected within 45 days after receipt ofregulatory approvals.    FN provides loan collection, accounting, data processingand administrative services to the real estate industry. Reuter&#3;